HOTAI MOTOR CO June Sales Fall 6.84% (Table) : 2207 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-11T09:08:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/hotai-motor-co-june-sales-fall-6-84-table-2207-tt.html
HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 6.84% to NT$6,308,899,000 from NT$6,772,362,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales           6,308,899        6,772,362   
YOY%              -6.84%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           39,740,988       42,709,417  
YOY%              -6.95% 
=================================================================
 